{
  "text": "Some methods also improve a coarse 3d fluid simulation by solving the wave equation on the animated surface (using a grid representation [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] or a Lagrangian representation [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] [CITATION_6] [CITATION_7] ) to add high-frequency turbulence.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "17943200",
    "[CITATION_2]": "2408906",
    "[CITATION_3]": "13916776",
    "[CITATION_4]": "2036802",
